Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.79,0:01:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.44,0:01:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.74,0:01:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，合體準備，好了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.99,0:01:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧，良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.43,0:01:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5、4、3、2、1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.88,0:01:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,激光射線同步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.96,0:01:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5、4、GUNDAM B部件投下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.77,0:01:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核心戰鬥機變形、合體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.71,0:02:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然少年們團結一致對抗ZION軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.38,0:02:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,焦躁卻使他們的關係變得不融洽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.81,0:02:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但敵人的進攻卻不會因為少年們的關係而鬆懈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.00,0:02:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,『死鬥！White Base』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.12,0:02:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,電碼的意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.55,0:02:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，內文說在敖德薩作戰前要駐留原地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.22,0:02:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已翻查過多次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.23,0:03:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那人叫蘭巴，是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.13,0:03:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.16,0:03:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留駐同一地點很易被找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.90,0:03:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話雖如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.60,0:03:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起碼讓麥嘉和奧斯卡休息一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.14,0:03:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.37,0:03:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們兩人的工作時間是最長的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.14,0:03:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如讓我幫也參加好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.28,0:03:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩子的衫縫好了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.84,0:03:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,縫好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.18,0:03:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳也很辛苦呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.25,0:03:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為什麼不吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.25,0:03:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快關門吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.58,0:03:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否則我會逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.15,0:03:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別胡說！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.72,0:03:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知蘭巴定會再來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.82,0:03:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愈沒有機動戰士那人愈會來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.16,0:03:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定會！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.23,0:03:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要來便來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.56,0:03:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會用GUNDAM去應戰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.50,0:03:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打算怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.60,0:03:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我離開母艦也不錯啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.14,0:03:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真要這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.11,0:03:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯！不成嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.14,0:03:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正你們也不喜歡我留在母艦內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.01,0:03:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豈有此理！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.35,0:03:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是認真的吧！良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.98,0:04:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得瑪吉露達少尉曾說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.79,0:04:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說你可能是個有超能力的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.12,0:04:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時我還覺得她的說法正確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.96,0:04:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰料...你竟然？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.86,0:04:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有瑪吉露達少尉這樣說吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.80,0:04:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要教訓我就用自己的話來教訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.53,0:04:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙勞·波，走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.80,0:04:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.04,0:04:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你動怒是你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.81,0:04:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我亦有自己原則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.15,0:04:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想講幾句說話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.81,0:04:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.52,0:04:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，是關於阿姆羅的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.05,0:04:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長不是真心想要阿姆羅走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.72,0:04:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為何有這想法？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.82,0:04:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你要關住阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.33,0:04:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無非要他反省
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.83,0:04:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是對他仍存有希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.33,0:04:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.50,0:04:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最初是隊長說要調走阿姆羅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.03,0:04:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如今怎樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.34,0:04:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實阿姆羅是可以帶GUNDAM投靠ZION
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.01,0:04:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他並沒有這樣做...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.94,0:04:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.38,0:04:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長對他仍未死心呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.85,0:05:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.18,0:05:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅回母艦隻是暫時的思鄉病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.75,0:05:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，不覺得祇差點時間嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.72,0:05:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？良！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.89,0:05:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說阿姆羅？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.42,0:05:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.07,0:05:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭巴上尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.20,0:05:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德茲爾將軍有電報來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.60,0:05:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由馬·克貝上校那邊轉送過來的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.01,0:05:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈蒙！又有好消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.21,0:05:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,3個陸戰動腦筋的多姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.94,0:05:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說會送過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.11,0:05:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多姆？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.08,0:05:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那種重型的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.42,0:05:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈蒙，先離開這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.98,0:05:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到取得多姆回來後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.45,0:05:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上向木馬進行攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.49,0:05:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在基希莉亞屬下的馬·克貝部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.93,0:05:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擁有地球最多的礦物資源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.03,0:05:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一帶是馬·克貝的總部...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.74,0:06:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經被蘭巴知道得太多這附近礦山的秘密了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.17,0:06:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基希莉亞將軍將來統治ZION國時，此地的資源已被用盡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.39,0:06:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以千萬別給基連中將知道實際的情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.25,0:06:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.95,0:06:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後的事你知怎做吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.86,0:06:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.29,0:06:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他求我們增援的事如何推他？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你放心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.93,0:06:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭巴這人是不會想得到的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.53,0:06:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.20,0:06:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良 快起來！良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.73,0:06:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良！隼人他們走了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說甚麼？雪拉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.09,0:06:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人、凱、亞磊、麥司他們走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.64,0:06:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫我追他們回來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.94,0:06:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去追吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.22,0:06:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣死人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.29,0:06:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們全都一樣任性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.23,0:06:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，麻煩你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.49,0:06:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心！就算打暈他們也要抬回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，我也想一起去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.38,0:07:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很快便回來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.51,0:07:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人總不會說出心底話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.68,0:07:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們對阿姆羅似乎是偏心了些...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.88,0:07:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有時...是形勢所逼的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.72,0:07:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅不在時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.52,0:07:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為指揮者我感到很不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.19,0:07:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不安？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.72,0:07:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然妳也很能幹！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.33,0:07:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.53,0:07:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙不在時我感到的不安是絕大的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.49,0:07:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底為甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.82,0:07:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是A1了地點 沒錯吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.22,0:07:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.39,0:07:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經過了半小時！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.16,0:07:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,親愛的，他們來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.89,0:08:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！只是馬·克貝部隊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.83,0:08:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼！多姆送不到來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.30,0:08:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！對不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.87,0:08:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我們的補給艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.01,0:08:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在正要進入中亞細亞時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.64,0:08:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被敵軍擊落了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.24,0:08:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多姆也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.91,0:08:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊，我蘭巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.92,0:08:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論怎樣也會完成任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.05,0:08:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請轉告馬·克貝上校吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.95,0:08:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.81,0:08:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.10,0:08:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告辭！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.52,0:08:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.86,0:08:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所謂匹夫之勇就是指這種人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.43,0:08:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們回基地去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.23,0:08:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我們應該怎辦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.67,0:08:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正如妳所說，不必靠補給
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.80,0:08:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就用回...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.21,0:08:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就用回我們游擊戰術吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.28,0:08:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認為怎樣？古副官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.94,0:08:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上尉，手足們反而喜歡這樣！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.15,0:08:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.82,0:09:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於肯停下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.99,0:09:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.73,0:09:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果想參戰 也不一定要在母艦上才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.47,0:09:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要去參加聯邦部隊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.53,0:09:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是否想丟下隊長不理？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.87,0:09:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長有阿姆羅就可以了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.87,0:09:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說夠沒有 凱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.84,0:09:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得在母艦上已沒意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.51,0:09:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是無法改變的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.61,0:09:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.58,0:09:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蓋洛普先繞到木馬前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.52,0:09:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基爾的ZAKU會一同出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.42,0:09:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇利就在母艦後在衝上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.86,0:09:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈蒙負責高速戰車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.66,0:09:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和古副官就負責第1部隊及第2部隊的隊長任務！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.02,0:09:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.96,0:09:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.13,0:09:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！蓋洛普出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.20,0:09:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,查出木馬下落後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.53,0:09:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基爾及奇利離開蓋洛普出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.48,0:10:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到木馬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.72,0:10:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比估計中多推進10公哩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.02,0:10:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那好極了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.15,0:10:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZAKU，奇利30秒後由戰車出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.02,0:10:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈蒙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.06,0:10:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們上母艦後，妳可以離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.26,0:10:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,親愛的，你自己小心了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.50,0:10:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必動手打人吧，良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.17,0:10:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.51,0:10:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想用武力逼人就範？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.98,0:10:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你們不用拳頭就不會清醒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.98,0:10:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？什麼聲音！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.19,0:10:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伏下，別被發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.30,0:10:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種聲音似是蓋洛普呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.81,0:11:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道他們去進攻母艦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.34,0:11:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是蘭巴！這次不好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.51,0:11:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們回不回去就憑良心判斷吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.08,0:11:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.77,0:11:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZAKU，基爾！出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.96,0:11:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著是奇利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.83,0:11:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.68,0:11:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們回去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.88,0:11:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.87,0:11:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.07,0:11:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.78,0:11:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然冷起來...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.31,0:11:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.86,0:11:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真沒趣！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.81,0:12:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種風給我的感覺才是戰爭！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.86,0:13:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個男孩是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.50,0:13:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色機動戰士的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GUNDAM的駕駛員？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.24,0:13:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他果然是天才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.14,0:13:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他會如此對付我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.38,0:13:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，他們離母艦有多遠！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.21,0:13:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在仍未可以掌握
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但已經叫奧斯卡和麥嘉來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.22,0:13:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備火箭炮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.49,0:13:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊，開動主引擎動力！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.92,0:13:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，已準備！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.16,0:13:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再等1分20秒吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.96,0:13:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起！我們來遲了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.60,0:13:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開左右激光炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.17,0:13:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尾閘也要全開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.77,0:13:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵軍似乎不祇一台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.80,0:13:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.91,0:13:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開探測器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.87,0:13:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偵查敵軍情況！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.31,0:13:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在前方確定有蓋洛普
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.15,0:13:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但礙於山的阻隔，其它調查不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.18,0:13:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,升高母艦高度嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.48,0:13:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暫時還未可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.79,0:14:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開監視用攝影機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.49,0:14:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是蓋洛普！已進入射程！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.69,0:14:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主炮射擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.23,0:14:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.34,0:14:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炮台幹什麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.81,0:14:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有ZAKU出現！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.91,0:14:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快開炮！快開炮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.14,0:14:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長，GUNDAM可以出發了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.21,0:14:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.15,0:14:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左面有ZAKU呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.85,0:14:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人會在你出發時攻擊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.32,0:14:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.15,0:14:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！我會的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.49,0:14:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GUNDAM！出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙勞·波，放阿姆羅出來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.23,0:14:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,門鎖是3F6E，知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.37,0:14:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.57,0:14:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱的汽車在那邊正開過來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.21,0:14:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們在那裏甚麼也做不來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.71,0:15:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是良他們回來了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那邊，看到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.18,0:15:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊，將母艦升高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.52,0:15:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使甲板和山的高度一樣！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.75,0:15:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.19,0:15:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙勞·波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.56,0:15:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！你快出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.86,0:15:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GUNDAM呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.69,0:15:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉已用來出戰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.93,0:15:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去擔任左邊的炮位吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.03,0:15:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.40,0:15:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.10,0:15:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？那是甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.04,0:15:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰車！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.50,0:15:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了，是白兵戰用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.88,0:15:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們想用肉博戰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.88,0:15:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備由甲板返回母艦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.88,0:15:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看著！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.82,0:15:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們已回來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.96,0:15:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好極！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.96,0:15:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後面有兩架戰車過來這面！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.66,0:15:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.33,0:15:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是白兵戰用的戰車！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.96,0:15:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼？白兵戰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.83,0:15:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起！我遲了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.01,0:16:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉！妳要退後些才瞄準
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.75,0:16:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向後跳！對了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.42,0:16:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.26,0:16:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打中了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.06,0:16:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打中了！雪拉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.26,0:16:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母艦想逃走？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.53,0:16:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立即攻擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.04,0:16:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們從後面攻過來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.97,0:16:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良、凱，可以戰鬥的人快到後面阻止敵人侵入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.33,0:16:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麥嘉，奧斯卡 你們有鎗嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.88,0:16:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不是想搶佔母艦的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.65,0:16:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高速戰車不會靠這麼近的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.89,0:16:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說起來是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.93,0:17:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.70,0:17:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家上！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.51,0:17:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向抵抗力較弱地方攻過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.95,0:17:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家，準備上！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.54,0:17:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阻止他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.10,0:17:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別讓他們進入母艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.21,0:17:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不成，GUNDAM威力太大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.48,0:17:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很難祇消滅士兵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.15,0:17:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快些離開！走啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.82,0:17:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦！竟然有小孩子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.06,0:18:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快退後，否則會受傷的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.06,0:18:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快退後！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.97,0:18:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奧斯卡，你快去守著門口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.84,0:18:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別讓敵軍進來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.60,0:18:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.54,0:18:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以進去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.19,0:18:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,78號門已被突破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.86,0:18:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.13,0:18:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快到艦橋去佔領它！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.51,0:18:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳一拿起鎗我便殺妳！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.94,0:18:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快進去躲起來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.61,0:18:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.01,0:18:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.52,0:19:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你贏我只因為機動戰士的性能好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.53,0:19:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並不是你戰勝我的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.83,0:19:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.83,0:19:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豈有此理！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.50,0:19:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和雪拉交換駕駛GUNDAM吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.01,0:19:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後去第2控制消滅敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.98,0:19:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用甚麼方法？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.51,0:19:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使破壞母艦也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.65,0:19:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.07,0:19:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.20,0:19:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託了！阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.28,0:19:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.91,0:19:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.57,0:19:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在第2控制室！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.55,0:19:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.85,0:19:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是這裏全都是少年兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.86,0:19:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不覺得奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.86,0:19:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來雙方也人手不足呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.16,0:19:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.56,0:19:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.20,0:19:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直衝過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.47,0:19:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.80,0:19:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,切斷第一控制室的線路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.69,0:19:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.28,0:20:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公主...妳是公主...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.95,0:20:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點也不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳一定是佩茜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.19,0:20:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是忘了我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.49,0:20:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我曾是妳爸爸馬志翁的部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.99,0:20:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是賴孝忠的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.83,0:20:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫蘭巴！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.54,0:20:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然你知我是佩茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.94,0:20:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼仍拿鎗向著我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.84,0:20:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.17,0:20:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳怎會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.04,0:20:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉 避開！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.25,0:20:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，蘭巴，快停止！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.88,0:20:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公主！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.45,0:20:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，聽到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.69,0:20:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第2控制室已被攻佔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.12,0:20:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炸開它！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.55,0:20:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.79,0:20:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快和哈蒙聯絡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.46,0:20:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，已較好波長了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.23,0:20:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作戰已經失敗，你們快撤退！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.53,0:20:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上尉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.54,0:20:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈蒙，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.17,0:21:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經不能再戰下去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.91,0:21:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我蘭巴...已在戰爭中被遺忘了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.85,0:21:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公主她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.28,0:21:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生甚麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.49,0:21:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是機動戰士GUNDAM嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.19,0:21:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我作戰的對手全都是年青人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.39,0:21:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部都小過我一半年紀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.56,0:21:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是諷刺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.57,0:21:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到你們戰得這樣好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.94,0:21:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但做軍人最後的命運如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.88,0:21:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們好好看著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.79,0:21:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭巴！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.54,0:22:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈蒙小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.71,0:22:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭巴上尉已戰死了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.21,0:22:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別再打好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.02,0:22:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快射出控制室！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.34,0:22:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭巴上尉沒再有消息嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.37,0:22:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有，上次已是最後了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.34,0:22:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.18,0:22:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭巴...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.96,0:23:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭巴上尉...哈蒙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.83,0:23:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心一些！大家小心抬...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.41,0:23:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈蒙繼承了戰死的拉爾的遺志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.24,0:23:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以極少量武器逼近的哈蒙終於將擊倒GUNDAM嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.77,0:23:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在此危機中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.91,0:23:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良·保政的核心戰鬥機襲向哈蒙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.01,0:23:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.49,0:23:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一集 『深刻憎恨的激鬥』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.21,0:23:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能夠存活下去嗎？

